        <div class="cl-item"><strong>No wall damage</strong><span>We use protective pads and know how to pivot a stacked pair in narrow openings</span></div>
        <div class="cl-item"><strong>Vent duct is critical</strong><span>Kinked duct behind closet stack is the most common dryer issue across SoCal apartments</span></div>
        <div class="cl-item"><strong>Mold prevention</strong><span>We advise on closet ventilation and door-ajar habits that prevent gasket mold recurrence</span></div>
        <div class="cl-item"><strong>Leak priority</strong><span>Leaks in apartment laundry closets are treated urgently, damage below is a real concern</span></div>
